Fidelity & Deposit Company of Maryland, Plaintiff in Error, v. Park Trammell, Governor, for use, etc.. Defendant in Error. A Writ of Error to a Judgment of the Circuit Court within and for the County of Hillsborough. Lucas & Withers, for Plaintiff in Error; Dickenson & Dickenson, for Defendant in Error.

Writ of Error dismissed on motion of counsel for plaintiff in error at cost of plaintiff in error.
